OL,3,CInitial messaging on Covid shielding
OL,4,C'could have been more nuanced', CMO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FInitial messaging around shielding at
OL,8,Fthe height of the Covid-19 pandemic
OL,9,Fcould have been more nuanced, Northern
OL,10,FIreland's chief medical officer has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FClose to the start of the outbreak of
OL,14,Fthe pandemic in the UK in March 2020,
OL,15,Fscores of people who were considered
OL,16,Fto be clinically extremely vulnerable
OL,17,Fwere advised to remain at home to
OL,18,Fprotect themselves from the virus.
