OL,3,CInitial messaging on Covid shielding
OL,4,C'could have been more nuanced', CMO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSir Michael McBride, who still serves
OL,8,Fas Northern Ireland's chief medical
OL,9,Fofficer (CMO), was speaking as he gave
OL,10,Fevidence to the UK Covid-19 Inquiry.
OL,12,FDuring a full-day appearance, Sir
OL,13,FMichael was asked with the benefit of
OL,14,Fhindsight whether he felt he had got
OL,15,Fall the decisions right.
OL,17,FHe responded saying ultimately that
OL,18,Fwould be for the inquiry to determine.
