OL,3,CInitial messaging on Covid shielding
OL,4,C'could have been more nuanced', CMO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I think there were some issues
OL,8,Fbecause of the pace of events, I think
OL,9,Fthere were certainly some issues in
OL,10,Frelation to communications, for
OL,11,Finstance to those shielding in terms
OL,12,Fof how we conveyed information, how we
OL,13,Fconveyed information in a balanced way
OL,14,Fwhich allowed people to make choices
OL,15,Fabout what was important to them, to
OL,16,Fempower them," he said.
