OL,3,CInitial messaging on Covid shielding
OL,4,C'could have been more nuanced', CMO
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"It became very difficult later on
OL,8,Fwhen the harm-and-benefit analysis
OL,9,Fchanged to provide them with
OL,10,Fassurance, to the population of people
OL,11,Fwho had been shielding who were
OL,12,Fclinically extremely vulnerable and
OL,13,Flooking back, I think some of the
OL,14,Finitial messaging around that could
OL,15,Fhave been more nuanced.
