OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"That was something which I was
OL,8,Fconcerned about and was concerned
OL,9,Freally from May 2020 when I had
OL,10,Fcommissioned some research to seek the
OL,11,Fviews of people who had been shielding
OL,12,Fin terms of the impact it was having
OL,13,Fon them."
